

The files in this directory are:
================================

  newfunctions2.txt :  a listing of the new function prototypes

  gfx2.h :  the new header file for those functions
            new functions and their descriptions are after line 50

  gfx2.o :      the new .o compiled file
  gfx2_mac.o :  the new .o compiled file for mac's

  testgfx2.cpp :   simple program to test some of the basic new functions

  testpoly.cpp :   program to test the new drawing functions (polygon, ellipse, arc, etc.)
                   and the 'filled' versions of some of them
                   also shows how to set up an array of points for the polygon

  testcursors.cpp :  program to test a few new cursors (mouse pointers)

  testfont.cpp :   simple program to test using a font

  testfont2.cpp :  complex program to display a rectangle based on a font's details
                   (only useful if you want to pricesely identify a font's dimensions)

